### Get Prometheus Metrics
# The /metrics endpoint exposes all Prometheus metrics in text format
# This can be scraped by a Prometheus server for monitoring
GET http://localhost:5000/metrics
Accept: text/plain

###

### Health Check (generates metrics)
# This will increment the request counter and create histogram data
GET http://localhost:5000/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Test Locked Endpoint (generates DB lock metrics)
# This will track DB lock acquisition and duration
GET http://localhost:5000/api/test/locked
X-User-Id: 12345
Accept: application/json

###

### Check Metrics Again (see updated values)
GET http://localhost:5000/metrics
Accept: text/plain

###
